WEBVTT


00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.109
taking my front step from dero to hero 

00:00:02.110 --> 00:00:04.200
wasn't exactly on my bingo card this week

00:00:04.201 --> 00:00:06.114
But once I start something I struggle to stop 

00:00:06.115 --> 00:00:07.280
and at this point of my life

00:00:07.281 --> 00:00:09.260
I've given up trying to fight the impulses 

00:00:09.261 --> 00:00:10.320
and I just let them win

00:00:10.321 --> 00:00:11.960
it certainly keeps life interesting

00:00:11.961 --> 00:00:13.760
so I water blasted everything I could see

00:00:13.761 --> 00:00:15.380
Potted a new plant for the front step 

00:00:15.381 --> 00:00:17.000
and things were starting to take shape

00:00:17.001 --> 00:00:18.560
