00:00:18.561 --> 00:00:19.640
cause for some reason

00:00:19.641 --> 00:00:21.189
I thought it would be a good idea to 

00:00:21.190 --> 00:00:22.320
paint my own front door mat

00:00:22.321 --> 00:00:24.600
and it was significantly harder than I anticipated

00:00:24.601 --> 00:00:25.583
but still heaps of fun 

00:00:25.584 --> 00:00:27.720
It would have been a lot easier if I'd made a stencil

