so despite the fact that I own the printer 

00:00:34.616 --> 00:00:35.200
and I own the ink

00:00:35.201 --> 00:00:37.066
apparently I have to pay a subscription 

00:00:37.067 --> 00:00:38.280
every month just to use it

00:00:38.281 --> 00:00:40.680
and that type of capitalism really fks me off to be honest

00:00:40.681 --> 00:00:42.320
but that's the story for another day anyway

