00:00:50.641 --> 00:00:52.240
when it dries I'll spray it with a sealer

00:00:52.241 --> 00:00:55.040
but while I was waiting I got distracted by shiny things

00:00:55.041 --> 00:00:56.680
or rather the lack thereof

00:00:56.681 --> 00:00:57.920
and I'm sure there are other people

00:00:57.921 --> 00:00:59.617
out there that suddenly find themselves in 

