00:01:07.041 --> 00:01:09.000
and this combo always works wonders for me 

00:01:09.001 --> 00:01:10.960
it was taking years of her life like honestly

00:01:10.961 --> 00:01:13.080
she was ageing backwards and by the time I was done

00:01:13.081 --> 00:01:15.127
they were quite shiny and I was feeling quite 

00:01:15.128 --> 00:01:16.240
accomplished to be honest

